ades. And, the gradebook does a great job of keeping student information confidential.\r\n\r\n<strong>Reorder and Delete Grades</strong>\r\n\r\nYou have full control over how you want to setup and interact with your gradebook. You can hide grades, reorder and delete grade items, create grade schemes, calculate final grades, adjust final grades, and transfer final grades to Banner.'),(36,14,'test',''),(37,14,'_test','field_50350f39eec0b'),(38,17,'_edit_last','1'),(39,17,'_edit_lock','1345658039:1'),(40,17,'tool_intro',''),(41,17,'_tool_intro','field_50350c167399d'),(42,17,'frequently_asked_questions',''),(43,17,'_frequently_asked_questions','field_50350c1673c29'),(44,17,'test',''),(45,17,'_test','field_50350f39eec0b'),(46,18,'_edit_last','1'),(47,18,'_edit_lock','1345658059:1'),(48,18,'tool_intro',''),(49,18,'_tool_intro','field_50350c167399d'),(50,18,'frequently_asked_questions',''),(51,18,'_frequently_asked_questions','field_50350c1673c29'),(52,18,'test',''),(53,18,'_test','field_50350f39eec0b'),(54,19,'_edit_last','1'),(55,19,'_edit_lock','1345658072:1'),(56,19,'tool_intro',''),(57,19,'_tool_intro','field_50350c167399d'),(58,19,'frequently_asked_questions',''),(59,19,'_frequently_asked_questions','field_50350c1673c29'),(60,19,'test',''),(61,19,'_test','field_50350f39eec0b'),(120,1,'_wp_trash_meta_status','publish'),(121,1,'_wp_trash_meta_time','1345724802'),(122,1,'_wp_trash_meta_comments_status','a:1:{i:1;s:1:\"1\";}'),(137,57,'_wp_attached_file','2012/08/initial-manage-grades.png'),(138,57,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:6:{s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"922\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"284\";s:14:\"hwstring_small\";s:23:\"height=\'39\' width=\'128\'\";s:4:\"file\";s:33:\"2012/08/initial-manage-grades.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:3:{s:4:\"file\";s:33:\"initial-manage-grades-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"150\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"150\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:3:{s:4:\"file\";s:32:\"initial-manage-grades-300x92.png\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"300\";s:6:\"height\";s:2:\"92\";